      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Prohibited Uses</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Scraping or automated collection of content from our website</li>
        <li>Using our content for commercial purposes without permission</li>
        <li>Attempting to hack, disrupt, or compromise our website</li>
        <li>Misrepresenting your identity when contacting us</li>
      </ul>

