      <p>Harmonium Halt shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the website or its content.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">External Links</h2>
      <p>Our website may contain links to external sites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@harmoniumhalt.com" class="text-saffron-600">hello@harmoniumhalt.com</a></p>
